Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Located along the main north-south thoroughfare in the quickly-growing, nationally recognized, booming suburb of Waukee, Iowa, this property is 9.03 acres and can meet the needs of any retailer or developer. Alice’s Road has been widened to six lanes and connects Hickman Rd/IA Hwy 6 to Grand Prairie Pkwy and the new I-80 interchange.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Land available for sale or for lease near the corner of Douglas and Alice’s Road. Seller will entertain a build to suit, sale or lease. Easy access to Alice’s Road/Grand Prairie Parkway and near residential and other commercial.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Grand Prairie Crossings is the area’s newest, premier commercial development offering a mix of high-end sites for Class-A office, Medical Office and Clinics, as well as, support retail for the neighborhood.  Centrally located at the crossroads of Grand Prairie and Westown Parkway in Waukee’s new Kettlestone town center, the site is being master planned to attract businesses looking for a fast growing area with amenities and infrastructure to support their growing business and long-term real estate plans.
